#: ../../source/SFD_ORA.rst:549
msgid "Canceled Responses"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/SFD_ORA.rst:551
msgid "If the course team deems a response that you have submitted to be inappropriate, they can cancel that response and remove it from peer grading. In the open response assessment you see an indicator that your submission was canceled, with the date and time of the cancellation, and a comment by the course team member about the reason."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/SFD_ORA.rst:557
msgid "The course team might allow you to submit a replacement response for the canceled one, or they might not. If they do not allow you to submit a replacement response, your grade is zero for the assignment."
msgstr ""
